# Design Token Usage Guide

This guide outlines the core design tokens defined for the Calm Home theme. When refactoring or writing new CSS, **always** prefer these variables over hardcoded values to ensure consistency and maintainability.

## Core Token Files

The base design tokens are defined in the following files:

*   [animations.css](mdc:assets/css/tokens/core/animations.css)
*   [borders.css](mdc:assets/css/tokens/core/borders.css)
*   [colors.css](mdc:assets/css/tokens/core/colors.css)
*   [shadows.css](mdc:assets/css/tokens/core/shadows.css)
*   [spacing.css](mdc:assets/css/tokens/core/spacing.css)
*   [typography.css](mdc:assets/css/tokens/core/typography.css)

## Whitelisted Variables

Use only the variables defined within these core files. Below is a summary (refer to the source files for exact values and context):

### Colors (`colors.css`)

*   **Hue/Saturation/Lightness:** `--hue-*`, `--sat-*`, `--light-lm-*`, `--light-dm-*`
*   **Backgrounds:** `--color-bg-base`, `--color-bg-alt`, `--color-bg-subtle`, `--color-surface`, `--color-surface-raised`
*   **Text:** `--color-text-primary`, `--color-text-secondary`, `--color-text-placeholder`, `--color-text-disabled`
*   **Primary Brand:** `--color-primary-fg`, `--color-primary-bg`, `--color-primary-bg-hover`, `--color-primary-bg-active`, `--color-on-primary`
*   **CTA/Accent:** `--color-cta-bg`, `--color-cta-bg-hover`, `--color-cta-text`, `--color-cta-bg-disabled`
*   **Borders:** `--color-border-strong`, `--color-border-medium`, `--color-border-subtle`, `--color-border-input`, `--color-border-focus`
*   **Feedback:** `--color-success-*`, `--color-error-*`, `--color-warning-*`, `--color-info-*` (includes fg, bg, text, border variants)
*   **Neutrals:** `--color-black`, `--color-white`, `--color-dark`, `--color-light`
*   **Brand Specific:** `--color-brand-primary`, `--color-brand-secondary`, `--color-brand-accent`
*   **Interactive:** `--color-interactive-*` (includes bg, border, text, hover variants)

### Spacing (`spacing.css`)

*   **Base Scale:** `--spacing-xs` to `--spacing-4xl`
*   **Containers:** `--container-xs` to `--container-max`
*   **Layout Gaps:** `--layout-gap-xs` to `--layout-gap-xl`
*   **Section Spacing:** `--section-spacing-sm` to `--section-spacing-lg`
*   **Forms:** `--input-height`, `--input-padding-*`, `--input-border-*`, `--input-focus-*`
*   **Buttons:** `--button-padding-*`, `--button-icon-spacing`, `--button-min-width`

### Typography (`typography.css`)

*   **Families:** `--font-family-base`, `--font-family-heading`, `--font-family-monospace`
*   **Sizes:** `--font-size-xs` to `--font-size-5xl`
*   **Weights:** `--font-weight-thin` to `--font-weight-black`
*   **Line Heights:** `--line-height-none` to `--line-height-loose`
*   **Letter Spacing:** `--letter-spacing-tighter` to `--letter-spacing-widest`
*   **Components:** `--modal-*`, `--email-*`, `--header-*`, `--footer-*`

### Borders (`borders.css`)

*   **Widths:** `--border-width-thin`, `--border-width-medium`, `--border-width-thick`
*   **Radii:** `--radius-none` to `--radius-full`, `--radius-soft`
*   **Components:** `--banner-*`, `--modal-*`, `--toast-*`, `--cart-*`

### Shadows (`shadows.css`)

*   **Base:** `--shadow-color`, `--shadow-color-hsl`
*   **Elevation:** `--shadow-xs` to `--shadow-2xl`, `--shadow-inner`
*   **Focus:** `--focus-ring-color`, `--focus-ring-width`, `--focus-ring-offset`, `--focus-ring`

### Animations (`animations.css`)

*   **Durations:** `--duration-instant` to `--duration-slow`
*   **Easings:** `--ease-default`, `--ease-in`, `--ease-out`, `--ease-bounce`
*   **Transitions:** `--transition-transform`, `--transition-opacity`, `--transition-colors`, `--transition-shadow`, `--transition-all`, `--transition-theme`
*   **Transforms:** `--scale-hover`, `--scale-active`, `--translate-hover`, `--translate-active`

## Usage Guidelines

*   **Prioritize Core Tokens:** Always attempt to use a variable from the `assets/css/tokens/core/` files first.
*   **Avoid Hardcoding:** Do not use literal pixel values, hex codes, or unitless numbers for properties managed by tokens (e.g., `color`, `font-size`, `margin`, `padding`, `border-radius`).
*   **Utility Tokens:** Variables in `assets/css/tokens/utility/` are acceptable for specific utility classes but should not replace core semantic tokens within component styles.
*   **Refactoring Goal:** Update existing component CSS (`assets/css/components/`, `assets/css/base/`, etc.) to use these core variables.

